title: HTC denies claims its One A9 handset is a clone of Apples iPhone
text:
HTC denies claims its One A9 handset is a clone of Apple's iPhone 
Daily Mail Saturday 24th October, 2015 
An executive from the Taiwanese firm has said that it was the first phone manufacturer to make a metal clad phone and Apple is the one that is copying its designs, not the other way round.?...
